						<summary>

						<p>Registers a sale of land to Śī (Śrī)[vīra] Kāladāsan of Pallapuram. Mentions the officer Rājēndrasiṅga Pallavaraiyan. The inscription is dated in the <hi rend="bold">48th year</hi> of the king's reign.</p>						

